Create a program that asks the user to write anything in the console (without using periods). 
Print out whatever they say, but add an exclamation mark at the end. 
Let the user be able to type answers in at least three times.

'''

entered = input("Enter anything that does not use periods")
print(entered + "!")
entered = input("Enter anything that does not use periods")
print(entered + "!")
entered = input("Enter anything that does not use periods")
print(entered + "!")
